&lt;h2 id=&#34;horizontal-rule&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#horizontal-rule&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; Horizontal Rule&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Three or more...&lt;/p&gt;
